reviews.title: Perfect for Portability
reviews.comment: This guide doesn\'t have maps or screen shots like full size guides tend to, but for a quick guide to pull up on your smartphone, this is perfect. :)
reviews.author: Nicholas Jabbour

reviews.title: Doesn\'t work; Rip off
reviews.comment: This app updated the day after I downloaded it. Now I have the icon on my screen, but when I click it it says that this app isn\'t downloaded on my phone. According to my phone and the app store it is on my phone. Rip off.
reviews.author: Nikki Zickafoose
